{
  "stem": "27543.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same thing, little villages, chopping woods, and bringing them in, bringing in, and unloading the carloads of stuff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a few things happen when we were in-- in-- in-- in Kremnitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, you know, you can have it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go in the warehouse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Give to me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do the same thing what I do to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bring in the village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They give you this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They bring you that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the-- three German officers come in to check-- I told you I worked in the warehouse too there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They come in to check the warehouse, missing this, missing that, missing that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So somebody said one of us-- the Jews must steal it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They said, they couldn't steal so much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beginning, it was 228.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From-- from-- from when I was?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think there was 10, 12.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was all kind of nationals there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was Polish Jews, Russian Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We find them there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just when I was in the [INAUDIBLE] in Lemberg, there was Polish Jews, Russian Jews, all kinds of Jews there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them prayed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never I-- I-- I said my pray at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told you what happened when we were in-- in-- in Kremnitz, Lebal asked somebody who don't want to work that day who wants to fast can have a day off.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- and then when he went up to the-- everybody was eating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have a day off then, I think, for three months or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was decent to us who don't want to work for Yom Kippur, can have that day off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was-- he was a prince.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lebal, the captain.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
